rows.label: tlk45710153_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I'm afraid I don't know anything
about any mechanical Blades.

rows.label: tlk45710153_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Anyway, is it just me, or is the air
a little oppressive in this city?

rows.label: tlk45710153_02_msg0003
rows.name:
There's sand blowing in from the
wastes outside, and the natural steam
makes the atmosphere so humid...

rows.label: tlk45710153_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I suppose I'm not used to
my own home after spending
so long in Goldmund.

rows.label: tlk45710153_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Would you believe I'm missing
the fresh air of my workplace?
